46
00:02:25.920 --> 00:02:26.880
Wow.

47
00:02:27.480 --> 00:02:28.320
Okay.

48
00:02:28.400 --> 00:02:30.360
[sheriff 2] There could
be something in here.

49
00:02:30.440 --> 00:02:32.160
[sheriff 1] Somebody needs
