15 years after its release.

85
00:04:27.000 --> 00:04:28.000
[girls screaming]

86
00:04:28.080 --> 00:04:29.200
[Randy] Without exaggeration.

87
00:04:29.280 --> 00:04:33.400
I think Michael was
the most famous person in the world.

88
00:04:33.480 --> 00:04:34.880
All the amazing talent.

89
00:04:34.960 --> 00:04:36.960
[crowd screaming]

90
00:04:39.400 --> 00:04:43.160
But then. you know.
you began to see the changes in him.

91
00:04:43.760 --> 00:04:47.160
[woman] I mean. let's face it.
he's a little weird.

92
00:04:47.240 --> 00:04:49.000
You know? He's just a little weird.

93
00:04:49.080 --> 00:04:52.160
[unsettling music playing]

94
00:04:52.240 --> 00:04:54.560
[Randy] The media was terrible
to Michael Jackson.

95
00:04:54.640 --> 00:04:57.080
With all the Wacko Jacko stuff.
which was horrible.

96
00:04:57.680 --> 00:05:00.200
{\an8}"What's with the hyperbaric chamber?"

97
00:05:00.280 --> 00:05:02.000
"What's with the plastic surgery?"

98
00:05:02.080 --> 00:05:05.360
{\an8}And Michael. he felt like
he was lonely and isolated.

99
00:05:05.440 --> 00:05:08.560
But he was determined
to live his life his way.

100
00:05:09.720 --> 00:05:12.000
Michael became friends
with all these kids.

101
00:05:12.080 --> 00:05:15.760
You know. he didn't think it was strange.
but other people did.

102
00:05:17.800 --> 00:05:21.240
{\an8}A 13-year-old boy alleges a sexual
relationship with Michael Jackson.

103
00:05:21.320 --> 00:05:23.360
[unsettling music continues]

104
00:05:23.440 --> 00:05:27.600
The idea of Michael Jackson being
a pedophile was. like. mind-blowing.

105
00:05:27.680 --> 00:05:31.200
It was the most far-fetched.
ridiculous thing you could have imagined.

106
00:05:32.120 --> 00:05:35.920
The pop star angrily rejected
accusations he molested a young boy.

107
00:05:36.000 --> 00:05:38.280
and lashed out at police and the media.

108
00:05:38.360 --> 00:05:43.000
{\an8}There have been many
disgusting statements made recently

109
00:05:43.080 --> 00:05:46.480
{\an8}concerning allegations
of improper conduct on my part.

110
00:05:46.560 --> 00:05:48.960
