are totally false.

111
00:05:49.040 --> 00:05:52.480
[Randy] After all these
terrible allegations about Michael.

112
00:05:52.560 --> 00:05:56.400
he had a hard time not just artistically.
but personally too.

113
00:05:56.480 --> 00:05:58.680
I saw the hell
that it had inflicted on him.

114
00:05:58.760 --> 00:06:00.480
He was so traumatized by that time.

115
00:06:01.280 --> 00:06:02.800
He needed. like. a reset.

116
00:06:02.880 --> 00:06:05.680
