some of these issues

117
00:06:05.760 --> 00:06:08.000
and his image in the public eye.

118
00:06:08.920 --> 00:06:11.920
- [music fades]
- [birds singing and chirping]

119
00:06:12.920 --> 00:06:14.920
[pensive music playing]

120
00:06:16.040 --> 00:06:20.720
[man] The first time I met Michael.
in London. June 2002â€¦

121
00:06:23.000 --> 00:06:25.360
